BOWER-GIEBEL WHOLESALE COMPANY, Appellant, v. SEARS-ROEBUCK & COMPANY, Appellee. No. 11236. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Nov. 22, 1946. Jerome D. Rolston, of Hollywood, Cal., for appellant. John L. Wheeler, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before MATHEWS, STEPHENS, and ORR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court, 69 F.Supp. 158, is affirmed.
